## Ent workspace

This workspace uses [Ent](https://github.com) kit at `ent/`. Open the **workspace root** (parent of `ent/`), not `ent/` alone.

Onboard: run `/ent-onboard` or:

```bash
node ent/tools/ent.mjs scaffold --workspace-root .
node ent/tools/ent.mjs audit --workspace-root .
```

<!-- ent:end -->
